e come across just about every demand there can be!<\/p>\n<h2>Some jobs we&#8217;ve worked on<\/h2>\n<p>We have some great feature films under our belts alongside a mix of TV and commercial catering contracts. For example, a few gigs we\u2019ve worked on include: <strong>X-Factor<\/strong>, <strong>The Brits<\/strong>,\u00a0<strong>Netflix productions,<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>BBC dramas<\/strong> including The Child in Time and Silent Witness, as well as travelling to Kazakhstan with <strong>Top Gear<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>We\u2019ve also worked on the UK launch of Australia\u2019s #1 cooking programme, <strong>My Kitchen Rules<\/strong>, where we fed a whole host of talented chefs, including Raymond Blanc, Prue Leith and Michael Caines.<\/p>\n<p>Click the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.imdb.com\/search\/title\/?companies=co0399714\">IMDb<\/a> link below to see more of our work.[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8268&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; onclick=&#8221;custom_link&#8221; link=&#8221;http:\/\/www.imdb.com\/company\/co0399714\/?ref_=ttco_co_2&#8243;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8262&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8267&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8731&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2>Our Packaging<\/h2>\n<p>Coronavirus is presenting new challenges in location catering. With greater demand for individually packaged take-away style meals, we&#8217;ve updated our range of packaging.<\/p>\n<p>We&#8217;re researching and testing various sturdy, recyclable consumables to make sure our food stays hot and secure. See some examples <a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/tv-film-catering\/our-packaging\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here<\/a>.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text] Location Caterers for TV &amp; Film Stars of the screen love the Radish\u2026 At the end of 2015 we bought a couple of catering trailers and went showbiz,&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/tv-film-catering\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":8731,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":9,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-templates\/template-no-sidebar.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-7724","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Location Catering for TV, Film &amp; Commercials - Red Radish<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"London-based reliable and creative location catering for TV and film. Bespoke menus, craft services and high quality food for your cast and crew.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/tv-film-catering\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Location Catering for TV, Film &amp; Commercials - Red Radish\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"London-based reliable and creative location catering for TV and 